#: ../../source/api/data_types.rst:2
msgid "管理历史数据的类型——DataType对象"
msgstr "Historical Data Types - DataType Object"

#: ../../source/api/data_types.rst:4
msgid ""
"DataType 用于以「名称 + 频率 + 资产类型」三元组的方式描述单一历史数据类型，是 数"
"据管线与策略声明历史数据需求时的统一语言。qteasy 预置了大量常用 DataType， 也支"
"持通过文档中介绍的接口定义用户自定义数据类型。"
msgstr ""
"DataType is used to describe a single historical data type as a triplet of "
"“name + frequency + asset type”. It is the common language for the data "
"pipeline and for strategies to declare historical data requirements. qteasy "
"comes with many commonly used DataTypes and also supports defining user-defined "
"data types via the interfaces described in the documentation."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:1
msgid "qteasy 中用于描述单一历史数据类型（名称、频率与资产类型）的核心对象。"
msgstr ""
"The core object in qteasy used to describe a single historical data type (name, "
"frequency, and asset type)."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:3
msgid ""
"每个 DataType 由 ``name``、``freq`` 和 ``asset_type`` 三要素唯一确定，可用于 统"
"一声明策略所需的数据、驱动 ``get_history_data_from_source()`` 等内部取数流程， "
"并在需要时扩展出自定义数据类型。关于完整的数据类型表与自定义流程，见文档 "
"「DataType 与历史数据类型管理」章节。"
msgstr ""
"Each DataType is uniquely determined by three elements: ``name``, ``freq``, and "
"``asset_type``. It can be used to uniformly declare the data required by a "
"strategy, drive internal data-fetching workflows such as "
"``get_history_data_from_source()``, and extend to custom data types when "
"needed. For the complete data type table and the customization process, see the "
"documentation chapter “DataType and Historical Data Type Management”."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:9
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Example"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:10
msgid ""
"下面示例展示 DataType 类名（稳定输出）。实际创建 DataType 时，需要提供 name/"
"freq/asset_type："
msgstr ""
"The example below shows the DataType class name (stable output). When actually "
"creating a DataType, you need to provide name/freq/asset_type:"

#: of qteasy.DataType.asset_type:1 qteasy.DataType.asset_type_str:1
msgid "资产类型的字符串表示形式，如'E'或'E,IDX'"
msgstr "String representation of asset types, such as 'E' or 'E,IDX'"

#: of qteasy.DataType.asset_types:1
msgid "所用用户定义的资产类型列表"
msgstr "The list of user-defined asset types used"

#: of qteasy.DataType.data_table_names:1
msgid ""
"获取数据表名称，优先使用用户定义的数据表名称，如果没有用户定义的数据表名称，则使"
"用内置数据表名称"
msgstr ""
"Get the data table name. Prefer the user-defined data table name; if no user-"
"defined data table name is provided, use the built-in data table name."

#: of qteasy.DataType.dtype_id:1
msgid "形如：close_E_d"
msgstr "In the form: close_E_d"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:1
msgid ""
"数据类型在一天之内开始可用的时间，如收盘价在15:00可用，开盘价在9:30可用，高频数"
"据没有可用时间"
msgstr ""
"The time within a day when the data type becomes available. For example, the "
"closing price is available at 15:00, the opening price is available at 9:30, "
"and high-frequency data has no availability time."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:4
msgid "Properties"
msgstr "Properties"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:5
msgid "asset_type: str"
msgstr "asset_type: str"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:6
msgid ""
"资产类型，如'E'、'IDX'、'FD'等，因为现在支持多资产类型，所以需要指定资产类型以获"
"取对应的可用时间"
msgstr ""
"Asset type, such as 'E', 'IDX', 'FD', etc. Since multiple asset types are now "
"supported, you need to specify the asset type to obtain the corresponding "
"availability time."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:1
msgid ""
"Datatype类从DataSource类获取数据的方法，根据数据类型的获取方式，调用相应的方法获"
"取数据并输出"
msgstr ""
"Method for the Datatype class to retrieve data from the DataSource class. "
"Depending on how the data type is retrieved, it calls the corresponding method "
"to fetch the data and output it."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:3
msgid "如果symbols为None，则输出为un-symbolised数据，否则输出为symbolised数据"
msgstr ""
"If symbols is None, the output is un-symbolised data; otherwise, the output is "
"symbolised data"

#: ../../source/api/data_types.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:5
msgid "数据类型对象"
msgstr "Data type object"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:7
msgid "股票代码列表，一个逗号分隔的字符串，如'000001.SZ,000002.SZ'"
msgstr ""
"A list of stock symbols, a comma-separated string such as '000001.SZ,000002.SZ'"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:9
msgid "开始日期, YYYYMMDD格式"
msgstr "Start date, in YYYYMMDD format"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:11
msgid "结束日期, YYYYMMDD格式"
msgstr "End date, in YYYYMMDD format"

#: of qteasy.DataType.id:1
msgid "忽略数据频率的ID形如：close(E)，用于标记不同资产类型的数据"
msgstr ""
"IDs that ignore data frequency look like: close(E), used to mark data for "
"different asset types."

#: of qteasy.DataType.unsymbolized:1
msgid ""
"return True if this data type is unsymbolized data type (i.e. reference data "
"type)"
msgstr ""
"return True if this data type is unsymbolized data type (i.e. reference data "
"type)"

#~ msgid "DataType class, 代表qteasy可以使用的历史数据类型。"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "DataType class, represents the historical data types that qteasy can use."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "qteasy的每一个历史数据类型由三组参数定义： - name: 数据类型的名称 - freq: 数"
#~ "据的频率 - asset_type: 数据的资产类型 以上三组参数唯一地定义了一个数据类型。"
#~ "qteasy定义了大量常用的数据类型，用户可以直接使用这些数据类型，也可以根据自己"
#~ "的需求定义新的数据类型。 如果用户自定义新的数据类型，三组参数不能与已有的数据"
#~ "类型重复。"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Each historical data type in qteasy is defined by three sets of parameters: "
#~ "- name: the name of the data type - freq: the frequency of the data - "
#~ "asset_type: the asset type of the data The above three sets of parameters "
#~ "uniquely define a data type. qteasy defines a large number of commonly used "
#~ "data types, which users can use directly, or define new data types according "
#~ "to their needs. If the user defines a new data type, the three sets of "
#~ "parameters cannot be duplicated with existing data types."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "用户在自定义数据类型时，需要指定数据类型的描述、数据获取方式、以及获取数据的"
#~ "参数。详情参见qteasy文档。"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "When defining a custom data type, the user needs to specify the description "
#~ "of the data type, the method of obtaining the data, and the parameters for "
#~ "obtaining the data. For details, see the qteasy documentation."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "一旦定义了数据类型，该数据类型就可以被qteasy用于历史数据的下载、处理、分析，"
#~ "也可以直接被用于交易策略的开发。"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Once the data type is defined, it can be used by qteasy for downloading, "
#~ "processing, and analyzing historical data, and can also be used directly for "
#~ "the development of trading strategies."

#~ msgid "需要获取数据时，通过DataType.get_data_from_source()方法获取。"
#~ msgstr "Use DataType.get_data_from_source() method to obtain data when needed."
